---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/about-hero.webp';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Toolbase"
	description="Honest AI tool reviews for solopreneurs. No fluff, no paid placements, no listicle filler."
	pubDate={new Date()}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Why Toolbase exists</h2>
	<p>
		There are more "best AI tools" listicles than there are actually useful AI tools.
		Most of them are SEO bait, affiliate links wrapped around shallow descriptions
		written by someone who never opened the software. We've all clicked one, scrolled
		through it, and left more confused than when we started.
	</p>
	<p>
		Toolbase is built around one rule: <strong>we only review tools we'd actually
		use ourselves to run a one-person business.</strong> That means real testing,
		real workflows, honest "this doesn't work" calls when warranted, and
		head-to-head comparisons that go beyond marketing screenshots.
	</p>

	<h2>Who this is for</h2>
	<p>
		Toolbase is for the solo operator, freelancers, indie founders, consultants,
		one-person agencies, side-hustle builders. People who don't have a procurement
		team or a marketing department, and who need their tool stack to actually pay
		for itself in saved hours or earned revenue.
	</p>
	<p>
		If you've ever spent a Saturday evaluating "the right" project management tool
		instead of doing client work, this site is for you.
	</p>

	<h2>What's next</h2>
	<p>
		New articles every week. Comparison guides, workflow tutorials, free
		utilities we build ourselves. Browse <a href="/blog">the blog</a> or
		follow along as we grow this thing.
	</p>
</Layout>
